Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.46,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.46,0:00:04.51,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'll always be your partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.51,0:00:06.11,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The car the three of us are riding in
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.11,0:00:07.98,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}is rigged to explode if we lower our speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.98,0:00:08.71,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What do we do, old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:10.65,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.69,0:00:12.40,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid\Nbut has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:14.45,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.41,0:01:46.54,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,♪ Chasing after rabbits… ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.54,0:01:50.17,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,♪ in Kano Mountain… ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.59,0:01:54.21,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,♪ Fishing for little fish… ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.21,0:01:58.68,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,♪ in Kano River… ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.43,0:02:02.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:04.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How many more kilometers\Nuntil we get to the hot springs?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.27,0:02:07.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still about 100 kilometers, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.06,0:02:11.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? We've only traveled for 10?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.85,0:02:12.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.80,0:02:14.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do you keep asking every five minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.67,0:02:16.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get that you're excited, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.16,0:02:18.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you be paying\Nattention to our speed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.82,0:02:20.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.49,0:02:22.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But today's going to be a great day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.95,0:02:26.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First is the hot springs...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:28.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then a delicious meal, and some good booze.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.79,0:02:31.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I'll enjoy it even more\Nsince it's half price!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:45.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Put me through to Inspector Megure, with the\NMPD's First Criminal Investigation Division, Section 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.35,0:02:49.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, get that for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:52.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's it from?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:53.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:54.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:56.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you say Inspector Megure?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:02:57.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.57,0:02:59.28,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Mouri{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-kun{\r\be10}! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:01.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-In Takaoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.00,0:03:04.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.14,0:03:07.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm in a car right now\Nwith my dad and Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.23,0:03:08.74,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ran{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-kun{\r\be10}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.74,0:03:09.83,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}In Takaoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:11.79,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Their current location is Takaoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:14.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd the inspector say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:15.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.48,0:03:16.81,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Listen up, Ran{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-kun{\r\be10}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.81,0:03:17.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:19.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remain calm and listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:21.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That car you're in...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:22.47,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That car you're in...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:27.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a bomb wired to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.27,0:03:28.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A bomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.45,0:03:31.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.46,0:03:32.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.17,0:03:39.07,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Once you've driven more than 10 kilometers,\Nthe bomb in that car will switch on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.51,0:03:42.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,10 kilometers?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:50.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means, the switch is already...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:53.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That car...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:55.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do not stop that car!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.05,0:03:57.75,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You have to keep moving forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:04:02.09,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}As soon as your speed falls below 20 km/h...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.88,0:04:04.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:06.68,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It seems that's how the criminal wired it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.70,0:04:24.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Inspector, couldn't this be a prank?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.74,0:04:33.59,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The criminal claimed he would blow up\Nthe water tower first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:37.26,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Since we can't confirm\Nif the threat is true or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.26,0:04:40.72,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We should assume that\Nthere really {\i1}is{\i0} a bomb attached.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.48,0:04:43.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}An explosion...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:44.95,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.70,0:04:49.92,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Since it exploded just as\Nthe old man happened to pass it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.92,0:04:52.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The bomb must have been\Nequipped with a timer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.67,0:04:58.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was a demonstration\Nto prove this wasn't a trick or a prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.39,0:05:03.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There really {\i1}is{\i0} a bomb in this car.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.44,0:05:15.61,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Mouri{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-kun{\r\be10}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:18.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:19.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keep calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.61,0:05:20.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just drive calmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.00,0:05:25.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've engaged emergency measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.52,0:05:30.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.03,0:05:50.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll try to catch up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:54.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.99,0:05:56.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have any intel on the bomber?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.08,0:05:59.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll tell you on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:03.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Earlier, a man called me,\Ngiving the name Sugiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.04,0:06:04.25,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Earlier, a man called me,\Ngiving the name Sugiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.25,0:06:05.55,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}While that's likely an alias,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:09.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he said that the car Kogoro Mouri rented\Nfrom Beika Rental Cars
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:11.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,had been fitted with a bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.73,0:06:14.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does someone named Sugiyama\Nbring anything to mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:16.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sugiyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.93,0:06:23.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The clerk from the rental service\Nwas named Sugiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:23.44,Signs,,0,0,0,,Beika Rental Cars
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:23.44,Signs,,0,0,0,,Jiro Sugiyama
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.27,0:06:29.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the one who referred us\Nto that 50% off hot spring deal today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.90,0:06:31.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:34.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said that if he was able to\Nkill a famous detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:36.91,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He said he'd become famous as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:39.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought it was a joke initially,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.58,0:06:41.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but he knew about your plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.84,0:06:44.34,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And after his display,\Nwith that water tower explosion...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.99,0:06:47.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have no choice\Nbut to follow his instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.59,0:06:48.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Instructions?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.97,0:06:49.84,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sugiyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:52.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wants you to get on the highway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:54.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The highway?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:55.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:56.56,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:58.06,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But until we have a better grasp of the situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:06:59.48,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}we should follow his instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:00.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:05.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The criminal called, and requested us by name to get on the highway... {cat: identified himself by name, and requested us to get on the highway}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:09.49,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Did he choose today for a specific reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:19.87,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Please report on the status of the blockade near the Takaoka entrance to the expressway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:25.14,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The entrance to the Gosho Highway from Takaoka,\Ntowards Araimachi, has now been closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:29.49,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Also, it has been sealed\Nin the Takaokamachi direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:36.05,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Route 8 has been sealed in the Takaoka entry direction, and detoured.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:40.60,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Footpaths adjacent to each road have also been sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:45.56,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Confirming sealing of all roads.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.22,0:07:49.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alternative routes have been ensured.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:50.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:52.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:55.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We located your car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:58.49,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Keep your car in the open lane.{cat: From now on, follow the white motorbikes.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:00.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:12.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, Conan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:14.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The inspector is already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:16.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police will help however they can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:17.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:20.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kogoro Mouri...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:23.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Writhe in terror!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.27,0:08:25.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll enjoy it, ever so slowly...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:26.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.45,0:08:33.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.04,0:08:35.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.85,0:08:37.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The gasoline...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:39.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's half gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:44.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I got the car, it was full!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:45.76,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.76,0:08:49.87,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The bomber must've waited for us to check, then emptied the tank just before we left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.87,0:08:51.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:53.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before we run out of gasoline,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:55.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll get the two of you out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:08:58.45,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Mouri{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-kun{\r\be10}, let the two of them out first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:08:59.79,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Open the windows!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:02.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They won't open!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:05.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Same with the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:07.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}, what about your side?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:09.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This side's no good either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:15.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn! They must have been sabotaged!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:20.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's less than half a tank of gasoline left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.57,0:09:24.87,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}At 20 km/h, we have one more hour at most.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:28.21,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Once the gasoline runs out,\Nthe car will stop and explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:33.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Since the windows and doors\Nwon't open from the inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:35.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What can we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:37.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Megure here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.52,0:09:39.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, where are you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.45,0:09:40.78,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.25,0:09:44.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure, sorry for the delay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.67,0:09:55.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We're depending on you, Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.83,0:10:00.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:02.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maintain this height!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:03.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:06.21,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm counting on you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.66,0:10:07.71,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.42,0:10:11.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:12.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get back from the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:22.89,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}While Ran and I can get out once\Nthe window glass is broken,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:24.89,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}what about the old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.46,0:10:27.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He'll have to take his foot off\Nthe accelerator to get out,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.77,0:10:29.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}which will cause the car to slow down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.66,0:10:35.11,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:40.11,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We can't let the car go below 20 km/h.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.11,0:10:41.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Will anything work?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:43.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Slow down!{cat: The tires!}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.74,0:10:44.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Back up!{cat: Keep them aligned!}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.99,0:10:47.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move the car back just a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.71,0:10:48.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.73,0:10:51.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The tires...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.08,0:10:52.29,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The tires?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:54.59,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The tires' spinning...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:57.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Stop without stopping them...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:02.97,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:12.01,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I have no other choice. I'll have to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.01,0:11:12.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.89,0:11:13.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.81,0:11:16.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Takagi, hurry up\Nand save me! I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.49,0:11:18.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just hold on, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:18.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.49,0:11:21.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to pull you over now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:31.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.71,0:11:32.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:37.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.75,0:11:40.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:42.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be OK. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:56.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They rescued one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:58.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:12:00.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In another ten minutes,\Nthe gasoline will be all used up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:03.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When that happens, Mouri will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.11,0:12:05.91,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Conan{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-kun{\r\be10} is safe and sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.07,0:12:09.43,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Next, we'll get Ran{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-san{\r\be10}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.43,0:12:10.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:11.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:12.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bad news!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.63,0:12:15.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're only few kilometers away\Nfrom a traffic jam.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.57,0:12:19.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's enough space\Nfor one car to make it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.79,0:12:21.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No more than that, even side-by-side.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.59,0:12:23.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Abort the rescue efforts!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:25.22,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Let's get on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:32.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:34.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.13,0:12:34.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.90,0:12:44.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.40,0:12:46.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.32,0:12:49.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.31,0:12:50.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi! Back up now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:51.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.88,0:13:04.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.77,0:13:06.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.29,0:13:08.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.46,0:13:10.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle Kogoro, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:33.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:37.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take my jacket and put it over your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.07,0:13:38.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roll after you jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.77,0:13:41.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You may get hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.31,0:13:43.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you won't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.01,0:13:44.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.89,0:13:46.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, what about you, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.67,0:13:48.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saving you comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.27,0:13:52.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just do this, for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.39,0:14:00.31,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Mouri{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-kun{\r\be10}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.31,0:14:02.00,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Can you hear me, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-kun{\r\be10}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.66,0:14:05.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Almost there...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.37,0:14:08.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're almost there, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.02,0:14:10.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ichiro Matsumiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.82,0:14:12.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.34,0:14:14.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a case that we worked on together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.96,0:14:19.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit murdered his ex-lover, and when trying to escape arrest,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:22.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he drove his bike onto the highway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.04,0:14:27.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He crashed into the safety railing and died, three years ago today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.17,0:14:32.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I thought that was suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:36.93,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Matsumiya had a younger brother\Nwho was studying in the US at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.93,0:14:38.60,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He didn't know the circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.60,0:14:42.81,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No matter how much we explained,\Nhe wouldn't believe it was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:44.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:46.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So this is revenge over a misunderstanding?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:50.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right now, we're looking for his brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.14,0:14:52.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll arrest him as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:53.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.90,0:14:55.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How much gasoline is left?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.10,0:14:59.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's almost empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.82,0:15:01.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know how long we have...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.70,0:15:04.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:08.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:09.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for getting you in this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:12.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:14.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry and jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.30,0:15:16.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:27.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.73,0:15:28.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.73,0:15:30.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Watch where you're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.48,0:15:37.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kogoro Mouri...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:39.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's almost time to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.86,0:15:42.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This tunnel...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.27,0:15:43.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will become your grave!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.17,0:16:36.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:38.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.50,0:16:40.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got Kogoro Mouri...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.82,0:16:41.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've avenged you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:43.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.84,0:16:53.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you going, if I may ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.89,0:16:57.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Megure, from the MPD.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:59.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jiro Matsumiya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, I believe?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:05.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was three years ago today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.87,0:17:11.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We looked into cases involving\NKogoro Mouri and the highway,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:15.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and found the death of your brother,\NIchiro Matsumiya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:17.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that he had a brother, Jiro Matsumiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:20.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how we got to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:22.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.51,0:17:28.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We suspect you used the computer in your house\Ntoday to hack into the highway department's security.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.68,0:17:32.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, we suspect it's\Nsomehow related to our case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.29,0:17:33.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you mind coming with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.58,0:17:40.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.24,0:17:42.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sugiyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:44.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, Matsumiya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:47.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You look like you just saw a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:48.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.83,0:17:51.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How... How are you still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.55,0:17:56.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I simply used the clues you left behind. {cat: I feel more alive than ever.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.09,0:18:00.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the car stopped,\Nit should've exploded!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.09,0:18:03.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We refueled the car, so it's still running.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:07.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's only a matter of time\Nuntil the bomb is disarmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:09.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:13.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wired it to the body!\NT-There's no way you could get to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.15,0:18:17.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The car kept moving without stopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.33,0:18:33.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The experts are disarming it as we speak...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:37.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While keeping the speed at 20 km/h.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.59,0:18:42.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, when...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.97,0:18:44.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about the explosion?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:45.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.76,0:18:47.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inside the tunnel...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.27,0:19:00.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bomb squad was hidden\Nin a large truck's cargo bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:04.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They set up a slope and a net...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:06.66,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We're all set.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.16,0:19:14.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once I reached the truck,\Nthey signaled me to drive the car inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:24.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once the car made it onto\Nthe truck bed, the net stopped it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.77,0:19:27.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,while tire rollers kept the tires spinning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:32.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, they were able to\Nmove in and rescue Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.01,0:19:34.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fill up the gas tank...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.00,0:19:36.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pry my door open...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.91,0:19:38.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And hold the accelerator in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.57,0:19:48.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This way, the tires kept spinning,\Neven though the car wasn't moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.95,0:19:52.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So they could take their time to disarm it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:54.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And using a smoke flare and fireworks...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.08,0:19:55.63,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Fire in the hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.84,0:20:00.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We made it seem like the car had exploded.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:01.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.69,0:20:03.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.92,0:20:06.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.67,0:20:10.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you all hadn't followed so closely...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.44,0:20:12.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My brother wouldn't have died...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:14.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.06,0:20:16.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your brother wanted to commit suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:18.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.52,0:20:21.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the reason my brother is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.61,0:20:24.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My brother wasn't some suicidal coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:28.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the scene of your brother's accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:30.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was no evidence\Nof the brakes being applied.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:32.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moreover, just before he crashed into the fence...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:35.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He took off his helmet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.21,0:20:37.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was intentional suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:38.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.42,0:20:39.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Matsumiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:41.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the one who won't listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.84,0:20:46.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you really think what you've done\Nwould make your late brother happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:47.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:48.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Matsumiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.93,0:20:51.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're lucky, compared to your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.97,0:20:54.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the end, no one died today...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:20:59.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means you didn't become\Na murderer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.73,0:21:03.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:05.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you're a lucky guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.90,0:21:07.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.45,0:21:12.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.93,0:22:52.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, I was really surprised
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.51,0:22:56.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when I saw that the person driving that enormous truck was actually Detective Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.64,0:23:00.56,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yes, it's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.35,0:23:03.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would you be surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.86,0:23:07.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} said you were\Nthe one who came up with the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.32,0:23:12.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.16,0:23:14.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should hurry to the hot springs!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.28,0:23:16.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no reason to do that now, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.49,0:23:19.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the half-price special was for today only!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.41,0:23:24.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unless he just made that up\Nto get us to take the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.38,0:23:26.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.75,0:23:30.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's possible that it just might be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.38,0:23:32.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And therefore, Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.80,0:23:34.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me borrow a police car.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.22,0:23:38.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you daft?\NHow could I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.77,0:23:39.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.52,0:23:42.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Always trying to find\Na bright side, eh, old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.99,0:23:50.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, let's head for the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.16,0:23:52.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.06,0:24:06.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.85,0:24:09.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? It won't open!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.56,0:24:10.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.56,0:24:16.56,Signs,,0,0,0,,On the next Conan:\NYoung Shin'ichi Kudo's Adventure\N(Part I)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.86,0:24:21.57,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint:
